description:
This is a set that includes the Arsenal "Prototype Arsenal", which allows you to change the appearance of your Arsenal, and the Outer Suit"Prototype Suit" that can be equipped by an Outer.

※These items are the same as the early purchase bonus content, "Prototype Arsenal" and "Prototype Suit".

※A copy of "DAEMON X MACHINA" is required to use this content.

※This content is not equipment, but items that change the appearance. There are no status changes associated with the use of these items.
name:
Arsenal "Prototype Arsenal"
Suit for Outer: "Prototype Suit" (Male & Female)
